dc_title_s: EMS Response Districts Lincoln County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Emergency Medical Service (EMS) response districts in Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2020.[This data set consists of digital data depicting the emergency service zones for Lincoln County, Wisconsin. ESZ locations were obtained provided by Lincoln County Land Information Office and is a combination of political city, town, and village boundaries and zip code bondaries. The zones are used to organize and dispatch emergency services to Lincoln County, Wisconsin. The Lincoln County Land Information Office plans to maintain this digital data in geodatabase format in an ESRI ArcSDE environment using ArcMap tools.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
